We recommended that the Municipal Mayor to: Submit explanation why the procurement of cellphones was done through reimbursement instead of public bidding;

enforce the direct payment to suppliers/creditors through check for all procurement of good pursuant to above provision. Limit the amount of expenses subject for reimbursements; and

